manifest.name: TickTick Quick Add Task
manifest.description: Create TickTick tasks from text blocks with automatic Obsidian URI links. Requires Advanced URI plugin.
manifest.author: Muxin Li

data.manifestValue: Create TickTick tasks from text blocks with automatic Obsidian URI links. Requires Advanced URI plugin.
data.communityListValue: Instantly creates a TickTick task from the current block of text using a keyboard shortcut. Task includes a copy of the text, and the URI to that exact block of text in your notes. Requires Advanced URI plugin.
